item.title: Around the island with Xeon Kayak Ergometer
item.description: February 5, 2023 88 nautical miles, or 164 Km Stats Xeon is a heavy-use Kayak Ergometer, that gives a true feel of on-the-water paddling. Xeon ergometer shaft to paddle length The correct way to manage fear is to gradually broaden your comfort zone until your comfort zone includes things that seemed previously impossible. Alex Honnold _
